text: Diane Delano (January 29, 1957 â€“ December 13, 2024) was an American actress. She was known for her roles in movies and television. She played Sergeant Barbara Semanski on the CBS television series Northern Exposure and Roberta "Bobbi" Glass on The WB television series Popular. She played Sister Beech in the 2006 movie The Wicker Man. Delano was born in Los Angeles, California.
